{"tid":978827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抱著牠直到斷氣…攝影師拍下「寵物安樂死瞬間」飼主撫屍哭斷腸","createTime":"2019-01-12T08:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T08:22:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c77383f400f5fc7c373dc374c1f55da966ccf08","tid":978827,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVpy6jV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVpy6jV.png&h=6b9f7e73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqgxCrB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqgxCrB.png&h=67b61764&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4n8Vdj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4n8Vdj.png&h=5955dabb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CSHZE0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CSHZE0.png&h=fa4cb258&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hT6tVdm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhT6tVdm.png&h=15105166&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DL2dmTo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDL2dmTo.png&h=4d728cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDXdmTp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDXdmTp.png&h=6a5ce1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Hd8aMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Hd8aMM.png&h=674a94a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVbhOyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVbhOyt.png&h=eff3890f&s={SIZE}\" />各位飼主們，或許都和粉粿一樣，我們都得理性成熟地告訴自己，有一天，毛孩們會比我們早一步離去。當那一天來臨，我們該如何面對、承受？<br />\n<br />\n美國攝影師Ross Taylor為了紀錄下飼主與寵物之間的深厚情感，探討人與動物間的親密關係，她接洽幾位打算讓生病毛小孩安樂死的飼主，邀請他們成為鏡頭前的主角，紀錄下毛小孩安樂死的過程。<br />\n<br />\nRoss同時和安樂死機構「Lap of Love」合作，得到飼主們的同意才拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n在Ross的照片中可以發現，幾位飼主都讓毛小孩「在家中安樂死」，對此，Ross表示，「讓寵物在充滿熟悉氣味的環境執行安樂死，這是簡單而平靜的過程，寵物在飼主懷中離去，對牠們是更人道、更好的方式。」<br />\n<br />\n看著幾位飼主在毛小孩離去後傷心欲絕的模樣，實在叫人難受！<br />\n<br />\n終將有一天，我們要面對毛小孩預先離去的事實，但，粉粿要叮嚀飼主們，務必站在毛孩的立場思考，別讓牠擔心、害怕、緊張，更別讓牠處於恐慌的狀態下，走上人生最後一哩路&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請飼主們務必珍惜，和毛小孩相處的每一天！對牠們來說，我們就是全世界。<br />\n<br />\n延伸影音...<br />\n<br />\nVIA rosstaylor<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40969?from=fb_et_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F40969%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_news&d=b8z1wYmQJIBDRJKllPC092owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=cf7ef0c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40969?from=fb_et_news</a>"},{"pid":"f10ecdff5492f143be30abea984b3532e6bad98a","tid":978827,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738c15c2c0c2d2cfecb6a633dcd552715fd760b0","tid":978827,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}